    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《<strong>杯杯倒满 Feed the Cups</strong>》将使您身入其境的体验一家饮品店的点点滴滴。您将在各式各样的饮品店中工作，根据顾客的需求尽可能的正确制作饮品，同时还要管理<strong>库存</strong>与<strong>进货</strong>，避免<strong>资金</strong>短缺，以及管控所能够承受的“<strong>压力</strong>”。游戏目前支持2人本地或远程同乐，以及2-4人的好友在线合作模式！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/6f2b927c0fdce210d6a79aace30a8cb7.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=174 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款轻度Roguelite饮品制作的游戏。您需要根据所销售的饮品类型：进行<strong>备料</strong>、为顾客<strong>点单</strong>、<strong>制作</strong>饮品、<strong>出杯</strong>、甚至打扫店铺卫生、应对市监局审查等等。游戏中所包含的饮品种类繁多，豆制，茶类，奶类，咖啡，气泡，苏打等等会随着关卡的推进逐步呈现。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/ea5986da9e9cf3c50b5a04d9fdbd080b.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=143 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/9f5f36ce6457c94faffe0b58a84aa854.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=143 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/a75def573107a52c0e1fcb6492f17510.poster.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/a75def573107a52c0e1fcb6492f17510.webm?t=1758506725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 想要开一家奶茶店吗？冰爽可口的柠檬水，醇厚甜蜜的珍珠奶茶，丰富口感的抹茶奶绿，全都从你的手中诞生。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/bd45095ba9ce4c51119824e3fc1259d9.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=143 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/4eed75564301a6f9243345f8c6092c83.poster.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/4eed75564301a6f9243345f8c6092c83.webm?t=1758506725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个人忙不过来？喊上你的男/女朋友，基友伙伴，一起来做奶茶吧！什么？有人偷偷在摸鱼？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/cc1fa3e4eb37dac69d707ad5dfe17130.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=143 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/b91ea0ef16aafcaf21a7f0473c099e7d.poster.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/b91ea0ef16aafcaf21a7f0473c099e7d.webm?t=1758506725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随机出现不同效果的挑战契约，会给你今天带来效果不一的buff，当然了，越好的效果需要付出的代价就越大哦~ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/06f0daa41c6c7de51eb362d45a5a3f0c.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=143 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/95da52c3ced347fefb8a6fd7e61eacfc.poster.avif?t=1758506725\" width=600 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2336220/extras/95da52c3ced347fefb8a6fd7e61eacfc.webm?t=1758506725\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每局游戏都会收获满满一堆的杯币，按比例换算成钞票，来买家具和升级房屋咯~！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人游戏也会按比例结算。放心，温馨奶茶店，不会当黑心老板让你打白工的！</p>",
